  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2b9283b6054aa4443b51ec1cd5098042, type: 3}
  m_Name: QuestionChoice3
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionChoiceData
  Question: You prepare to leave for the Eternal Garden, but the Wolf begins to follow
    closely, stepping into your personal space. "Wait! I'm still feeling a bit of
    'noise.' I need to stay right next to you to feel better."
  option1: I understand you're agitated, but I need you to stay here while I go to
    my sanctuary. I am setting a boundary.
  option2: Okay, you can follow me just this once since you're feeling overwhelmed.
  option3: I'll run as fast as I can so you can't keep up with me
